case_address_found_1: WOODED AREA NEAR INTERSECTION OF HIGHWAY 49 AND ONEAL ROAD
case_circumstances: On February 22, 2006 utility crews were clearing the wooded area near the intersection of Highway 49 and Oneal road. While clearing the area a tent was found in the woods. Inside the tent was a body in advanced stages of decomposition. Estimated time of death was December 15, 2005. Left thumb print was of comparison quality.
case_head_hair: Dark brown to black hair approximately 14"-16" long.
